Another 4-2 score for the Parisiens, this time after their visit to Brest, at the Stade Francis Le-Blé thanks to Ander Herrera (23'), Kylian Mbappe (36'), Idrissa Gueye (73') and Angel Di Maria (90'). Franck Honorat (42') and Steve Mounie (85') scored the two goals for Brest.
